      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·頌·商頌·003.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">玄鳥.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>天命玄鳥，降而生商，宅殷土芒芒。古帝命武湯，正域彼四方。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Heaven commissioned the swallow,
To descend and give birth to (the father of our) Shang.
(His descendants) dwelt in the land of Yin, and became great.
(Then) long ago God appointed the martial Thang,
To regulate the boundaries throughout the four quarters (of the kingdom).</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__song-shangsong-003__002__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sbe-v3-1879">
      <prop type="x-work-id">shijing</prop>
