      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·頌·商頌·003.3</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">玄鳥.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>武丁孫子，武王靡不勝。龍旂十乘，大糦是承。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The descendant of Wû-ting
Is a martial sovereign, equal to every emergency.
Ten princes, (who came) with their dragon-emblazoned banners,
Bear the large dishes of millet.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__song-shangsong-003__004__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sbe-v3-1879">
