      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·頌·商頌·003.4</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">玄鳥.4</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>邦畿千里，維民所止，肇域彼四海。四海來假，來假祁祁。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The royal domain of a thousand lî
Is where the people rest;
But the boundaries that reach to the four seas commence there.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__song-shangsong-003__005__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sbe-v3-1879">
