      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·頌·商頌·003.5</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">玄鳥.5</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>景員維河，殷受命咸宜，百祿是何。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>From the four seas they come (to our sacrifices);
They come in multitudes.
King has the Ho for its outer border.
That Yin should have received the appointment (of Heaven) was entirely right;—
(Its sovereign) sustains all its dignities.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
